item.title: Fortescue induction - Tetra radio
item.description: Types of radios Vehicle Based Radio Vehicle Based Radio Power on Power Off To turn Off the radio Press and hold the mode button for 6 seconds until the radio shuts down. The MODE BUTTON is the power button. Hand Based Console Key and Button Functions The 0 key is for the screen change from day to night mode for better viewing and less glare.
